OL,3,CBakery marks renewal of New Ferry
OL,4,Ceight years after gas explosion
OL,6,FITV News' Andy Bonner went to speak
OL,7,Flocals in New Ferry as they visited
OL,8,Fthe bakery.
OL,10,FThere has always been hope that New
OL,11,FFerry would rise "like a phoenix" from
OL,12,Fthe rubble of a gas explosion that
OL,13,Fripped apart an already declining area
OL,14,Fof Wirral.
OL,16,FThat rise could be symbolised, not by
OL,17,Fa mythical creature, but the baked
OL,18,Fpies and sausage rolls coming out of
OL,19,Fthe ovens at the newly re-opened
OL,20,FGriffiths bakery.
