OL,3,CBakery marks renewal of New Ferry
OL,4,Ceight years after gas explosion
OL,6,FThe much-loved local baker was one of
OL,7,Fmany destroyed in the explosion caused
OL,8,Fby alocal business owner who set off
OL,9,Fthe blast in an attempt to claim
OL,10,Finsurance in March 2017.
OL,12,FEighty one people were injured. Blasio
OL,13,Fwas jailed for 19 years.
OL,15,FEight years on, Griffiths bakery has
OL,16,Fre-opened and greets queues of
OL,17,Fcustomers every morning when the
OL,18,Fshutters go up.
