OL,3,CBakery marks renewal of New Ferry
OL,4,Ceight years after gas explosion
OL,6,FCo-owner Ritchie Hyland says there
OL,7,Fhave been tough times here, but there
OL,8,Fare signs of renewal.
OL,10,FThe business had been set up by Dave
OL,11,FGriffiths and has been in New Ferry
OL,12,Ffor decades. Sadly Dave died this year
OL,13,Faged 78. His daughter is running it
OL,14,Fnow. She says her father would be
OL,15,Foverwhelmed and proud.
