OL,3,CBakery marks renewal of New Ferry
OL,4,Ceight years after gas explosion
OL,6,F"He was never the same after that
OL,7,Fexplosion and he just wanted to get
OL,8,Fback to work and get back up and
OL,9,Frunning. It was his life. It was what
OL,10,Fhe wanted to do, just get re-opened
OL,11,Fbut he didn't make it because he
OL,12,Fpassed away'.
