OL,3,CBakery marks renewal of New Ferry
OL,4,Ceight years after gas explosion
OL,6,FThere are also new one and two-
OL,7,Fbedroomed houses on the site of the
OL,8,Fexplosion itself with planning
OL,9,Fpermission in place for further
OL,10,Fdevelopment. Wirral council has
OL,11,Fsecured government funding and is
OL,12,Fpromising to spend more than #5
OL,13,Fmillion pounds on improving the high
OL,14,Fstreet.
OL,16,FProgress has been slow causing some
OL,17,Ffrustration but those queueing for a
OL,18,FGriffiths pie are largely glad to see
OL,19,Fthings happening in the area.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
