OL,3,CBakery marks renewal of New Ferry
OL,4,Ceight years after gas explosion
OL,6,F"You can see from the queues that
OL,7,Fthings are improving, " says one
OL,8,Fcustomer.
OL,10,F"It had been like a ghost town really
OL,11,Fso this is great because you can see
OL,12,Fpeople back out," says another waiting
OL,13,Fto buy a pie.
OL,15,FAnd another who remembers Griffiths
OL,16,Fbefore the explosion says, "It was
OL,17,Falways in everybody's hearts in the
OL,18,Farea. Hopefully this will inspire the
OL,19,Flocal area now".
